1. *Alkohol* je veoma štetan za zdravlje. (Alcohol is very detrimental to health.)
2. *Alkohola* se ne sme zloupotrebljavati. (Alcohol must not be abused.)
3. On je mnogo popio *alkohola* preko večeri. (He drank a lot of alcohol throughout the evening.)
4. Ona prodaje *alkohol* u maloj prodavnici. (She sells alcohol in a small shop.)
5. On je popio previše *alkohola* i nije bio u stanju da se kreće. (He had drunk too much alcohol and was unable to move.)
6. Oni su govorili o zloupotrebi *alkohola*. (They were talking about the misuse of alcohol.)
7. On se nije pridržavao ograničenja na unos *alkohola*. (He did not comply with the restrictions on alcohol intake.)
8. *Alkoholom* se ne sme zloupotrebljavati. (Alcohol must not be abused.)